lead_paragraph: Girondins Bordeaux have agreed a deal for their Tunisia winger Wahbi Khazri to move to Sunderland, the Ligue 1 club said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Sunderland Agree Deal With Bordeaux for Winger Khazri
